# SEBI ADJUDICATION ORDER – BBD SOFTWARE COM LTD
**Order No.:** WTM/AB/IVD/123/2024-25  |  **Date:** 18 Nov 2024
**Violation:** Insider trading by CTO (sold 2% stake 3 days before missed earnings)
**Penalty:** ₹4.2 Cr + 3-year market ban for CTO
**Status:** Appeal pending; no escrow/reserve created in books

**Discrepancy Flag:** Material undisclosed contingent liability + banned key executive